comment: /**  * Set the username of the user that should enabled or disabled. Must not be {@code null}  */
code: /**  * Set the username of the user that should enabled or disabled. Must not be {@code null}  */ public SetEnabledRequestBuilder username(String username) {     request.username(username).     return this. }

comment: /**  * Set whether the user should be enabled or not  */
code: /**  * Set whether the user should be enabled or not  */ public SetEnabledRequestBuilder enabled(boolean enabled) {     request.enabled(enabled).     return this. }
